
1  

Ido kapaaran kaŋin ikamunete aŋor akanykaarei ekiliokit ediopet, kobalasi ebe, “Kinyamenenei isio inyamatakosi, kinapenenei da inapene kosi: konye kisiikinai konyarai sio ekonikiror; kolema ijo amorositikosi.”


2  

Kapaaran kaŋin eraun atenut naka EJAKAIT naejok ido nakaibuses, eraunos da araito nuka akwap nukeitur nuejijimikinete ŋul luekuito luka Isirael. 
3  Kosodi kanen, ŋolloideuna koSion, ka ŋol loesalakinit Yerusalem enyarao lokalaunan, ŋes ŋinituŋanan yeniwadikatai araut yenikajaran koYerusalem: 
4  naedaunia EJAKAIT ailotar amodokok kere naka apesur nuka Sion, aitesegar da aokot nuka Yerusalem kokidiŋike, kanuka emoyo loka etube, ido kanuka emoyo loka aicwe. 
5  

Ido esubakini EJAKAIT ŋolitogo kere loka emoru Sion ka atukonokinetake, edou ka apuru paaran, ka aica naka akim naesarani kuare: naarai eterakini eiswapet aibuses kere. 
6  Ejaun da ewema araun etolim lokapaaran kanuka aibuse, amecis ka aŋopis kanuka akaka ka akiru.

